; Coverage test for select.cc line 267: thus_far += " + " for date column
; When a date column is NOT the first column in a select query,
; the thus_far accumulator needs to prepend " + " before adding
; "int(date_width) + 1". This exercises the true branch of:
;   L266: if (!thus_far.empty())
;   L267: thus_far += " + "

2024/01/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

test select amount, date from posts
      $50.00 24-Jan-15
     $-50.00 24-Jan-15
end test
